@node "QuickSetup" "   Quick Installation   "
@next "Main"
@prev "Main"
 Quick Installation:
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

 1. Copy the LineID Directory to the Doors directory as defined
    in MEBBSNet.
 2. Place the following lines in your Logon.[txt] file(s).

    Start ----->

      ~v!DOOR/DOORS:LineID/LineID#

      ~vc 

    <---- End

 3. Read the complete documentation for information on customizing LineID.
@endnode

